value.0: A portrait of the late wife and mother of Lord Arsant Wiltun and their daughter, Lady Oilanna.  It is the supposedly the last portrait left of the Jarlin, and Oilanna resembles her greatly.
Portrait of the Late Jarlin, Julianna of Wiltun. Beloved wife and mother.  Requiescat In Pace.
